_sText:
refix final 13/03/2017 (ladder bug in server)

I made this map, it's created 100% by me. It's about the SuperMario Bros Game. It has all kinds of games, and is very controllable with some CounterTerrorist.

Games:
Burned
Career
Clock
Reed floor
Colors
Bhoop
Footbal
Basketball

This map do not work in version v34 of counter strike source.
If you see the map bright, go to video / advanced, and change the option HDR to: NO HDR
